nodes.text: A pilot served in the Resistance during its war with the First Order. In 35 ABY, this pilot served under the callsign Alpha Three in the climatic Battle of Exegol, where the pilot was shot down and killed.
The Resistance pilot using the callsign "Alpha Three" was briefly mentioned in the 2019 sequel trilogy film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker.
